px-3 py-3 text-base text-fg-muted hover:text-fg rounded-md hover:bg-fg/5\">المسيرة</a></li><li><a href=\"#gallery\" class=\"block px-3 py-3 text-base text-fg-muted hover:text-fg rounded-md hover:bg-fg/5\">المعرض</a></li><li><a href=\"#contact\" class=\"block px-3 py-3 text-base text-fg-muted hover:text-fg rounded-md hover:bg-fg/5\">تواصل</a></li><li class=\"mt-2\"><a href=\"#contact\" class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center w-full px-4 h-11 rounded-md text-sm font-medium text-white border border-gold-soft bg-maroon\">تواصل معنا</a></li></ul></div></div></header><main class=\"relative\"><section id=\"top\" class=\"relative isolate overflow-hidden pt-32 pb-24 md:pt-40 md:pb-32\"><div aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"absolute inset-0 -z-10 hero-glow\"></div><div aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"absolute inset-0 -z-10 bg-qatari-dots opacity-60 [mask-image:radial-gradient(ellipse_at_center,black_40%,transparent_75%)]\"></div><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-10\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center\"><div class=\"lg:col-span-7\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full border border-gold-soft bg-bg-elev/60 backdrop-blur-sm\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(14px)\"><span class=\"h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-gold\"></span><span class=\"text-[11px] tracking-[0.22em] uppercase text-gold\">رئيس قسم · ترشيد · كهرماء</span></div><h1 class=\"mt-7 font-display text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-[68px] leading-[1.06] tracking-tight text-fg text-balance\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)\">نقود وعياً مستداماً لمستقبل قطر</h1><p class=\"mt-6 max-w-2xl text-base md:text-lg text-fg-muted text-pretty\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px)\">قيادي قطري يشغل منصب رئيس قسم في برنامج ترشيد، يساهم في جهود الحفاظ على الموارد وكفاءة استخدام الطاقة والمياه ودعم أهداف الاستدامة الوطنية انسجاماً مع رؤية قطر الوطنية 2030.</p><div class=\"mt-9 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(14px)\"><a href=\"#about\" class=\"group inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-5 h-12 rounded-md text-sm font-medium text-white bg-maroon hover:bg-maroon-strong border border-gold-soft transition-colors shadow-[0_8px_30px_-12px_rgba(0,0,0,0.45)]\">عرض الملف<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-0.5 flip-rtl\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a><a href=\"#contact\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-5 h-12 rounded-md text-sm font-medium text-fg border border-border-strong hover:bg-fg/5 transition-colors\">تواصل</a></div><div class=\"mt-10 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-x-8 gap-y-3 text-xs tracking-wide text-fg-subtle\" style=\"opacity:0\"><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-map-pin text-gold\"><path d=\"M20 10c0 4.993-5.539 10.193-7.399 11.799a1 1 0 0 1-1.202 0C9.539 20.193 4 14.993 4 10a8 8 0 0 1 16 0\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"10\" r=\"3\"></circle></svg>الدوحة، قطر</span><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"h-1 w-1 rounded-full bg-gold-soft\"></span>كهرماء · ترشيد</span><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"h-1 w-1 rounded-full bg-gold-soft\"></span>منسجم مع رؤية قطر الوطنية 2030</span></div></div><div class=\"lg:col-span-5\"><div class=\"relative mx-auto max-w-md\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px) scale(0.98)\"><div aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"absolute -inset-3 rounded-[22px] border border-gold-faint\"></div><div class=\"relative aspect-[4/5] rounded-[18px] overflow-hidden glass-strong\"><img alt=\"مهند اليافعي — رئيس قسم، ترشيد\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1024px) 32vw, (min-width: 640px) 60vw, 90vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fportrait.jpeg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=%2Fportrait.jpeg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=%2Fportrait.jpeg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fportrait.jpeg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fportrait.jpeg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fportrait.jpeg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fportrait.jpeg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fportrait.jpeg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fportrait.jpeg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fportrait.jpeg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fportrait.jpeg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/><div aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"absolute inset-x-0 bottom-0 h-1/3 bg-gradient-to-t from-bg/70 to-transparent\"></div><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 22 22\" class=\"absolute text-gold/70 top-3 left-3\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M1 8 V1 H8\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"></path><circle cx=\"1\" cy=\"1\" r=\"0.8\" fill=\"currentColor\"></circle></svg><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 22 22\" class=\"absolute text-gold/70 top-3 right-3 rotate-90\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M1 8 V1 H8\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"></path><circle cx=\"1\" cy=\"1\" r=\"0.8\" fill=\"currentColor\"></circle></svg><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 22 22\" class=\"absolute text-gold/70 bottom-3 left-3 -rotate-90\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M1 8 V1 H8\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"></path><circle cx=\"1\" cy=\"1\" r=\"0.8\" fill=\"currentColor\"></circle></svg><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 22 22\" class=\"absolute text-gold/70 bottom-3 right-3 rotate-180\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M1 8 V1 H8\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"></path><circle cx=\"1\" cy=\"1\" r=\"0.8\" fill=\"currentColor\"></circle></svg></div><div class=\"mt-5 glass rounded-xl px-4 py-3 flex items-center justify-between\"><div><p class=\"text-[10px] tracking-[0.24em] uppercase text-fg-subtle\">حالياً</p><p class=\"text-sm text-fg mt-0.5\">رئيس قسم · ترشيد</p></div><span class=\"h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-sage shadow-[0_0_0_4px_rgba(123,168,151,0.15)]\"></span></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"about\" class=\"relative py-24 md:py-32\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-10\"><header class=\"mb-12 md:mb-16 max-w-3xl\"><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-5 \"><span class=\"h-px w-8 bg-gold/70\"></span><span class=\"text-xs tracking-[0.28em] uppercase text-gold font-medium\">نبذة</span></div></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><h2 class=\"font-display text-3xl md:text-5xl leading-[1.1] tracking-tight text-balance text-fg\">قيادي قطري ملتزم بخدمة الوطن.</h2></div></header><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 lg:gap-16\"><div class=\"lg:col-span-7\"><div class=\"space-y-6 text-[17px] leading-[1.85] text-fg-muted text-pretty\"><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><p>قيادي قطري في القطاع العام يعمل ضمن برنامج ترشيد — البرنامج الوطني للحفاظ على الطاقة وكفاءتها التابع لكهرماء. يتمحور عمله حول القيادة، ورفع الوعي العام، والإدارة المسؤولة لموارد قطر الطبيعية.</p></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><p>بصفته رئيس قسم، يقود فريقاً متعدد التخصصات يركز على الاتصال الاستراتيجي، والتفاعل المجتمعي، ومبادرات الاستدامة المتوافقة مع رؤية قطر الوطنية 2030. ويجمع نهجه بين الانضباط التشغيلي والتزام عميق بالوطن وأهله ومستقبله.</p></div></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><div class=\"mt-10 hairline-gold h-px w-full\"></div></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><p class=\"mt-6 font-display text-xl md:text-2xl text-gold italic\">“<!-- -->خدمة قطر هي أساس كل جهد — اليوم وللأجيال القادمة.<!-- -->”</p></div></div><div class=\"lg:col-span-5\"><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><div class=\"glass rounded-2xl p-2\"><dl class=\"grid grid-cols-2 divide-x divide-y divide-border overflow-hidden rounded-xl\"><div class=\"p-5 md:p-6\"><dt class=\"text-[10px] tracking-[0.26em] uppercase text-fg-subtle\">المنصب</dt><dd class=\"mt-2 text-base md:text-lg font-medium text-fg\">رئيس قسم</dd></div><div class=\"p-5 md:p-6\"><dt class=\"text-[10px] tracking-[0.26em] uppercase text-fg-subtle\">البرنامج</dt><dd class=\"mt-2 text-base md:text-lg font-medium text-fg\">ترشيد</dd></div><div class=\"p-5 md:p-6\"><dt class=\"text-[10px] tracking-[0.26em] uppercase text-fg-subtle\">الجهة</dt><dd class=\"mt-2 text-base md:text-lg font-medium text-fg\">كهرماء</dd></div><div class=\"p-5 md:p-6\"><dt class=\"text-[10px] tracking-[0.26em] uppercase text-fg-subtle\">المقر</dt><dd class=\"mt-2 text-base md:text-lg font-medium text-fg\">الدوحة، قطر</dd></div></dl></div></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><div class=\"mt-6 glass rounded-2xl p-6\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><span class=\"h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-sage\"></span><span class=\"text-xs tracking-[0.22em] uppercase text-fg-subtle\">التوافق الوطني</span></div><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm text-fg-muted leading-relaxed\">العمل بانسجام مع ركيزة التنمية البيئية في رؤية قطر الوطنية 2030 — لدعم نهج متوازن بين التنمية وإدارة الموارد.</p></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"leadership\" class=\"relative py-24 md:py-32\"><div aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"absolute inset-0 -z-10 bg-[radial-gradient(ellipse_at_top,var(--accent-maroon-soft),transparent_60%)]\"></div><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-10\"><header class=\"mb-12 md:mb-16 max-w-3xl\"><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-5 \"><span class=\"h-px w-8 bg-gold/70\"></span><span class=\"text-xs tracking-[0.28em] uppercase text-gold font-medium\">القيادة</span></div></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><h2 class=\"font-display text-3xl md:text-5xl leading-[1.1] tracking-tight text-balance text-fg\">دور قائم على المسؤولية والوعي والأثر.</h2></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><p class=\"mt-5 text-base md:text-lg text-fg-muted text-pretty max-w-2xl\">بصفته رئيس قسم، تمتد مسؤولياته لتشمل الاتصال، والتفاعل المجتمعي، وأولويات الاستدامة طويلة الأمد للبرنامج.</p></div></header><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-5\"><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><article class=\"group relative h-full glass rounded-2xl p-7 transition-all hover:border-gold-soft hover:bg-fg/[0.04]\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center h-11 w-11 rounded-lg bg-maroon-soft border border-maroon-soft text-gold\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.6\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-message-square\"><path d=\"M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z\"></path></svg></span><span class=\"text-[10px] tracking-[0.26em] uppercase text-fg-faint\">0<!-- -->1</span></div><h3 class=\"mt-6 font-display text-xl md:text-2xl text-fg tracking-tight\">الاتصال الاستراتيجي</h3><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-fg-muted\">صياغة رسائل واضحة وموثوقة تدعم أولويات الحفاظ الوطنية عبر مختلف الجمهور والقنوات.</p><div aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"absolute inset-x-0 bottom-0 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-gold-soft to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity\"></div></article></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><article class=\"group relative h-full glass rounded-2xl p-7 transition-all hover:border-gold-soft hover:bg-fg/[0.04]\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center h-11 w-11 rounded-lg bg-maroon-soft border border-maroon-soft text-gold\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.6\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-users\"><path d=\"M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2\"></path><circle cx=\"9\" cy=\"7\" r=\"4\"></circle><path d=\"M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87\"></path><path d=\"M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75\"></path></svg></span><span class=\"text-[10px] tracking-[0.26em] uppercase text-fg-faint\">0<!-- -->2</span></div><h3 class=\"mt-6 font-display text-xl md:text-2xl text-fg tracking-tight\">الوعي المجتمعي</h3><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-fg-muted\">تعزيز التفاعل العام لتحويل الوعي إلى عادات يومية في البيوت والمدارس والمؤسسات.</p><div aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"absolute inset-x-0 bottom-0 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-gold-soft to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity\"></div></article></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><article class=\"group relative h-full glass rounded-2xl p-7 transition-all hover:border-gold-soft hover:bg-fg/[0.04]\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center h-11 w-11 rounded-lg bg-maroon-soft border border-maroon-soft text-gold\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.6\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-leaf\"><path d=\"M11 20A7 7 0 0 1 9.8 6.1C15.5 5 17 4.48 19 2c1 2 2 4.18 2 8 0 5.5-4.78 10-10 10Z\"></path><path d=\"M2 21c0-3 1.85-5.36 5.08-6C9.5 14.52 12 13 13 12\"></path></svg></span><span class=\"text-[10px] tracking-[0.26em] uppercase text-fg-faint\">0<!-- -->3</span></div><h3 class=\"mt-6 font-display text-xl md:text-2xl text-fg tracking-tight\">مبادرات الاستدامة</h3><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-fg-muted\">دعم المبادرات التي تعزز الاستهلاك المسؤول والإدارة البيئية طويلة الأمد.</p><div aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"absolute inset-x-0 bottom-0 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-gold-soft to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity\"></div></article></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><article class=\"group relative h-full glass rounded-2xl p-7 transition-all hover:border-gold-soft hover:bg-fg/[0.04]\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center h-11 w-11 rounded-lg bg-maroon-soft border border-maroon-soft text-gold\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.6\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-compass\"><path d=\"m16.24 7.76-1.804 5.411a2 2 0 0 1-1.265 1.265L7.76 16.24l1.804-5.411a2 2 0 0 1 1.265-1.265z\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle></svg></span><span class=\"text-[10px] tracking-[0.26em] uppercase text-fg-faint\">0<!-- -->4</span></div><h3 class=\"mt-6 font-display text-xl md:text-2xl text-fg tracking-tight\">قيادة الفريق</h3><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-fg-muted\">قيادة قسم متعدد التخصصات بوضوح ومساءلة وثقافة خدمة عامة.</p><div aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"absolute inset-x-0 bottom-0 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-gold-soft to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity\"></div></article></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><article class=\"group relative h-full glass rounded-2xl p-7 transition-all hover:border-gold-soft hover:bg-fg/[0.04]\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center h-11 w-11 rounded-lg bg-maroon-soft border border-maroon-soft text-gold\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.6\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-droplets\"><path d=\"M7 16.3c2.2 0 4-1.83 4-4.05 0-1.16-.57-2.26-1.71-3.19S7.29 6.75 7 5.3c-.29 1.45-1.14 2.84-2.29 3.76S3 11.1 3 12.25c0 2.22 1.8 4.05 4 4.05z\"></path><path d=\"M12.56 6.6A10.97 10.97 0 0 0 14 3.02c.5 2.5 2 4.9 4 6.5s3 3.5 3 5.5a6.98 6.98 0 0 1-11.91 4.97\"></path></svg></span><span class=\"text-[10px] tracking-[0.26em] uppercase text-fg-faint\">0<!-- -->5</span></div><h3 class=\"mt-6 font-display text-xl md:text-2xl text-fg tracking-tight\">الحفاظ على الطاقة والمياه</h3><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-fg-muted\">المساهمة في برامج تحمي موارد قطر الحيوية من الطاقة والمياه للأجيال القادمة.</p><div aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"absolute inset-x-0 bottom-0 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-gold-soft to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity\"></div></article></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><article class=\"group relative h-full glass rounded-2xl p-7 transition-all hover:border-gold-soft hover:bg-fg/[0.04]\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center h-11 w-11 rounded-lg bg-maroon-soft border border-maroon-soft text-gold\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.6\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-flag\"><path d=\"M4 15s1-1 4-1 5 2 8 2 4-1 4-1V3s-1 1-4 1-5-2-8-2-4 1-4 1z\"></path><line x1=\"4\" x2=\"4\" y1=\"22\" y2=\"15\"></line></svg></span><span class=\"text-[10px] tracking-[0.26em] uppercase text-fg-faint\">0<!-- -->6</span></div><h3 class=\"mt-6 font-display text-xl md:text-2xl text-fg tracking-tight\">التنمية الوطنية</h3><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-fg-muted\">مواءمة أولويات القسم مع رؤية قطر الوطنية 2030 وأهداف التنمية الشاملة للدولة.</p><div aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"absolute inset-x-0 bottom-0 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-gold-soft to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity\"></div></article></div></div></div></section><section id=\"mission\" class=\"relative py-24 md:py-32\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-10\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 lg:gap-16\"><div class=\"lg:col-span-5\"><header class=\"mb-12 md:mb-16 max-w-3xl\"><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-5 \"><span class=\"h-px w-8 bg-gold/70\"></span><span class=\"text-xs tracking-[0.28em] uppercase text-gold font-medium\">المهمة</span></div></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><h2 class=\"font-display text-3xl md:text-5xl leading-[1.1] tracking-tight text-balance text-fg\">منسجم مع ترشيد وكهرماء ورؤية 2030.</h2></div></header><div class=\"space-y-5 text-[17px] leading-[1.85] text-fg-muted text-pretty max-w-xl\"><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><p>ترشيد برنامج وطني للحفاظ على الطاقة وكفاءتها في دولة قطر تحت مظلة كهرماء — المؤسسة العامة القطرية للكهرباء والماء. يعزز البرنامج الاستخدام المسؤول للطاقة والمياه في جميع أنحاء البلاد، دعماً للأهداف الوطنية في مجال الاستدامة وإدارة الموارد.</p></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><p>ضمن هذه المهمة، يساهم القسم في الوعي والاتصال والمبادرات المجتمعية — انسجاماً مع ركيزة التنمية البيئية في رؤية قطر الوطنية 2030.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"lg:col-span-7\"><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><div class=\"relative glass-strong rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-10 overflow-hidden\"><div aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"absolute -top-24 -right-24 h-64 w-64 rounded-full bg-maroon-soft blur-3xl\"></div><div aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"absolute -bottom-32 -left-20 h-72 w-72 rounded-full bg-gold-faint blur-3xl\"></div><div class=\"relative flex items-center gap-3\"><span class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center h-9 w-9 rounded-md border border-gold-soft bg-bg-elev/70\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-sparkles text-gold\"><path d=\"M9.937 15.5A2 2 0 0 0 8.5 14.063l-6.135-1.582a.5.5 0 0 1 0-.962L8.5 9.936A2 2 0 0 0 9.937 8.5l1.582-6.135a.5.5 0 0 1 .963 0L14.063 8.5A2 2 0 0 0 15.5 9.937l6.135 1.581a.5.5 0 0 1 0 .964L15.5 14.063a2 2 0 0 0-1.437 1.437l-1.582 6.135a.5.5 0 0 1-.963 0z\"></path><path d=\"M20 3v4\"></path><path d=\"M22 5h-4\"></path><path d=\"M4 17v2\"></path><path d=\"M5 18H3\"></path></svg></span><span class=\"text-[11px] tracking-[0.26em] uppercase text-gold\">ترشيد · كهرماء</span></div><p class=\"relative mt-6 font-display text-2xl md:text-3xl text-fg leading-snug text-balance\">الحفاظ على الموارد وكفاءة استخدام الطاقة لقطر — مدعومة بالوعي والاتصال والتفاعل المجتمعي.</p><div class=\"relative mt-8 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4\"><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><div class=\"rounded-xl border border-border bg-bg-elev/60 p-5 h-full\"><p class=\"text-[10px] tracking-[0.26em] uppercase text-gold\">الحفاظ على الموارد</p><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm text-fg-muted leading-relaxed\">دعم الوعي حول الاستخدام المسؤول للطاقة والمياه.</p></div></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><div class=\"rounded-xl border border-border bg-bg-elev/60 p-5 h-full\"><p class=\"text-[10px] tracking-[0.26em] uppercase text-gold\">الكفاءة</p><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm text-fg-muted leading-relaxed\">المساهمة في برامج تعزز الاستهلاك الفعّال عبر مختلف القطاعات.</p></div></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><div class=\"rounded-xl border border-border bg-bg-elev/60 p-5 h-full\"><p class=\"text-[10px] tracking-[0.26em] uppercase text-gold\">رؤية 2030</p><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm text-fg-muted leading-relaxed\">منسجم مع ركيزة قطر الوطنية للتنمية البيئية طويلة الأمد.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"values\" class=\"relative py-24 md:py-32\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-10\"><header class=\"mb-12 md:mb-16 text-center mx-auto max-w-3xl\"><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-5 justify-center\"><span class=\"h-px w-8 bg-gold/70\"></span><span class=\"text-xs tracking-[0.28em] uppercase text-gold font-medium\">القيم</span></div></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><h2 class=\"font-display text-3xl md:text-5xl leading-[1.1] tracking-tight text-balance text-fg\">مبادئ توجّه العمل.</h2></div></header><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-px bg-border rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-border\"><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><div class=\"group relative h-full bg-bg-elev/80 p-8 md:p-10 transition-colors hover:bg-bg-elev-2/50\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.6\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shield-check text-gold transition-transform group-hover:-translate-y-0.5\"><path d=\"M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z\"></path><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><h3 class=\"mt-5 font-display text-xl md:text-2xl text-fg\">النزاهة</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-fg-muted\">العمل بصدق وشفافية ومسؤولية أخلاقية.</p></div></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><div class=\"group relative h-full bg-bg-elev/80 p-8 md:p-10 transition-colors hover:bg-bg-elev-2/50\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.6\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-flag text-gold transition-transform group-hover:-translate-y-0.5\"><path d=\"M4 15s1-1 4-1 5 2 8 2 4-1 4-1V3s-1 1-4 1-5-2-8-2-4 1-4 1z\"></path><line x1=\"4\" x2=\"4\" y1=\"22\" y2=\"15\"></line></svg><h3 class=\"mt-5 font-display text-xl md:text-2xl text-fg\">خدمة قطر</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-fg-muted\">وضع الوطن وأهله في صميم كل قرار.</p></div></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><div class=\"group relative h-full bg-bg-elev/80 p-8 md:p-10 transition-colors hover:bg-bg-elev-2/50\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.6\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-leaf text-gold transition-transform group-hover:-translate-y-0.5\"><path d=\"M11 20A7 7 0 0 1 9.8 6.1C15.5 5 17 4.48 19 2c1 2 2 4.18 2 8 0 5.5-4.78 10-10 10Z\"></path><path d=\"M2 21c0-3 1.85-5.36 5.08-6C9.5 14.52 12 13 13 12\"></path></svg><h3 class=\"mt-5 font-display text-xl md:text-2xl text-fg\">الاستدامة</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-fg-muted\">حماية الموارد الطبيعية للأجيال الحاضرة والقادمة.</p></div></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><div class=\"group relative h-full bg-bg-elev/80 p-8 md:p-10 transition-colors hover:bg-bg-elev-2/50\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.6\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-lightbulb text-gold transition-transform group-hover:-translate-y-0.5\"><path d=\"M15 14c.2-1 .7-1.7 1.5-2.5 1-.9 1.5-2.2 1.5-3.5A6 6 0 0 0 6 8c0 1 .2 2.2 1.5 3.5.7.7 1.3 1.5 1.5 2.5\"></path><path d=\"M9 18h6\"></path><path d=\"M10 22h4\"></path></svg><h3 class=\"mt-5 font-display text-xl md:text-2xl text-fg\">الابتكار</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-fg-muted\">تبني الأفكار والتقنيات والأساليب الجديدة في الخدمة العامة.</p></div></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><div class=\"group relative h-full bg-bg-elev/80 p-8 md:p-10 transition-colors hover:bg-bg-elev-2/50\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.6\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-compass text-gold transition-transform group-hover:-translate-y-0.5\"><path d=\"m16.24 7.76-1.804 5.411a2 2 0 0 1-1.265 1.265L7.76 16.24l1.804-5.411a2 2 0 0 1 1.265-1.265z\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle></svg><h3 class=\"mt-5 font-display text-xl md:text-2xl text-fg\">القيادة</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-fg-muted\">القيادة بتواضع ووضوح وتفكير بعيد المدى.</p></div></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><div class=\"group relative h-full bg-bg-elev/80 p-8 md:p-10 transition-colors hover:bg-bg-elev-2/50\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.6\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-heart-handshake text-gold transition-transform group-hover:-translate-y-0.5\"><path d=\"M19 14c1.49-1.46 3-3.21 3-5.5A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 16.5 3c-1.76 0-3 .5-4.5 2-1.5-1.5-2.74-2-4.5-2A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 2 8.5c0 2.3 1.5 4.05 3 5.5l7 7Z\"></path><path d=\"M12 5 9.04 7.96a2.17 2.17 0 0 0 0 3.08c.82.82 2.13.85 3 .07l2.07-1.9a2.82 2.82 0 0 1 3.79 0l2.96 2.66\"></path><path d=\"m18 15-2-2\"></path><path d=\"m15 18-2-2\"></path></svg><h3 class=\"mt-5 font-display text-xl md:text-2xl text-fg\">الأثر المجتمعي</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-fg-muted\">بناء وعي يتحول إلى تغيير حقيقي ومستدام.</p></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"achievements\" class=\"relative py-24 md:py-32\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-10\"><header class=\"mb-12 md:mb-16 max-w-3xl\"><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-5 \"><span class=\"h-px w-8 bg-gold/70\"></span><span class=\"text-xs tracking-[0.28em] uppercase text-gold font-medium\">أبرز المحطات</span></div></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><h2 class=\"font-display text-3xl md:text-5xl leading-[1.1] tracking-tight text-balance text-fg\">أبرز المحطات المهنية الأخيرة.</h2></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><p class=\"mt-5 text-base md:text-lg text-fg-muted text-pretty max-w-2xl\">محطات نموذجية — يمكن استبدالها بتفاصيل موثقة بسهولة.</p></div></header><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 md:gap-5\"><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><div class=\"group flex items-start gap-4 glass rounded-xl p-5 md:p-6 hover:border-gold-soft transition-colors\"><span class=\"mt-0.5 inline-flex items-center justify-center h-8 w-8 rounded-md bg-maroon-soft border border-maroon-soft\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check text-gold\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg></span><div><p class=\"text-[10px] tracking-[0.26em] uppercase text-fg-faint\">محطة<!-- --> · 0<!-- -->1</p><p class=\"mt-1.5 text-base md:text-lg text-fg\">التعيين رئيساً للقسم</p></div></div></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><div class=\"group flex items-start gap-4 glass rounded-xl p-5 md:p-6 hover:border-gold-soft transition-colors\"><span class=\"mt-0.5 inline-flex items-center justify-center h-8 w-8 rounded-md bg-maroon-soft border border-maroon-soft\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check text-gold\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg></span><div><p class=\"text-[10px] tracking-[0.26em] uppercase text-fg-faint\">محطة<!-- --> · 0<!-- -->2</p><p class=\"mt-1.5 text-base md:text-lg text-fg\">دعم جهود الوعي الوطني بالحفاظ على الموارد</p></div></div></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><div class=\"group flex items-start gap-4 glass rounded-xl p-5 md:p-6 hover:border-gold-soft transition-colors\"><span class=\"mt-0.5 inline-flex items-center justify-center h-8 w-8 rounded-md bg-maroon-soft border border-maroon-soft\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check text-gold\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg></span><div><p class=\"text-[10px] tracking-[0.26em] uppercase text-fg-faint\">محطة<!-- --> · 0<!-- -->3</p><p class=\"mt-1.5 text-base md:text-lg text-fg\">العمل ضمن مبادرات ترشيد</p></div></div></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><div class=\"group flex items-start gap-4 glass rounded-xl p-5 md:p-6 hover:border-gold-soft transition-colors\"><span class=\"mt-0.5 inline-flex items-center justify-center h-8 w-8 rounded-md bg-maroon-soft border border-maroon-soft\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check text-gold\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg></span><div><p class=\"text-[10px] tracking-[0.26em] uppercase text-fg-faint\">محطة<!-- --> · 0<!-- -->4</p><p class=\"mt-1.5 text-base md:text-lg text-fg\">المساهمة في الاتصال المتمحور حول الاستدامة</p></div></div></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><div class=\"group flex items-start gap-4 glass rounded-xl p-5 md:p-6 hover:border-gold-soft transition-colors\"><span class=\"mt-0.5 inline-flex items-center justify-center h-8 w-8 rounded-md bg-maroon-soft border border-maroon-soft\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check text-gold\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg></span><div><p class=\"text-[10px] tracking-[0.26em] uppercase text-fg-faint\">محطة<!-- --> · 0<!-- -->5</p><p class=\"mt-1.5 text-base md:text-lg text-fg\">المشاركة في التعاون متعدد التخصصات</p></div></div></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><div class=\"group flex items-start gap-4 glass rounded-xl p-5 md:p-6 hover:border-gold-soft transition-colors\"><span class=\"mt-0.5 inline-flex items-center justify-center h-8 w-8 rounded-md bg-maroon-soft border border-maroon-soft\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check text-gold\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg></span><div><p class=\"text-[10px] tracking-[0.26em] uppercase text-fg-faint\">محطة<!-- --> · 0<!-- -->6</p><p class=\"mt-1.5 text-base md:text-lg text-fg\">التواصل مع الشركاء العامين والمؤسسيين</p></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"journey\" class=\"relative py-24 md:py-32\"><div aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"absolute inset-0 -z-10 bg-[radial-gradient(ellipse_at_bottom,var(--accent-gold-faint),transparent_60%)]\"></div><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-10\"><header class=\"mb-12 md:mb-16 max-w-3xl\"><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-5 \"><span class=\"h-px w-8 bg-gold/70\"></span><span class=\"text-xs tracking-[0.28em] uppercase text-gold font-medium\">المسيرة</span></div></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><h2 class=\"font-display text-3xl md:text-5xl leading-[1.1] tracking-tight text-balance text-fg\">مسيرة مهنية شكلتها روح الخدمة.</h2></div></header><div class=\"relative mt-4\"><div aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"absolute start-3 md:start-1/2 top-2 bottom-2 w-px bg-gradient-to-b from-transparent via-gold-soft to-transparent md:-translate-x-1/2\"></div><ol class=\"space-y-10 md:space-y-14\"><li class=\"relative\"><div class=\"md:grid md:grid-cols-2 md:gap-12 items-start\"><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><div class=\"relative ps-10 md:ps-0 md:pe-12 md:text-end\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"absolute top-1 start-0 md:start-auto md:top-2 h-6 w-6 rounded-full bg-bg-elev border border-gold-soft flex items-center justify-center md:-end-3\"><span class=\"h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-gold\"></span></span><p class=\"text-[10px] tracking-[0.26em] uppercase text-gold\">التعليم</p><h3 class=\"mt-2 font-display text-2xl md:text-3xl text-fg tracking-tight\">الأساس الأكاديمي</h3><p class=\"mt-3 text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-fg-muted max-w-md md:ms-auto\">بناء أساس متين في الاتصال والقيادة والخدمة العامة.</p></div></div></div></li><li class=\"relative\"><div class=\"md:grid md:grid-cols-2 md:gap-12 items-start\"><div class=\"hidden md:block\"></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><div class=\"relative ps-10 md:ps-0 md:ps-12\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"absolute top-1 start-0 md:start-auto md:top-2 h-6 w-6 rounded-full bg-bg-elev border border-gold-soft flex items-center justify-center md:-start-3\"><span class=\"h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-gold\"></span></span><p class=\"text-[10px] tracking-[0.26em] uppercase text-gold\">بداية المسيرة</p><h3 class=\"mt-2 font-display text-2xl md:text-3xl text-fg tracking-tight\">بدايات في القطاع العام</h3><p class=\"mt-3 text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-fg-muted max-w-md \">اكتساب خبرات في الأدوار المتصلة بالجمهور والمبادرات الوطنية.</p></div></div></div></li><li class=\"relative\"><div class=\"md:grid md:grid-cols-2 md:gap-12 items-start\"><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><div class=\"relative ps-10 md:ps-0 md:pe-12 md:text-end\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"absolute top-1 start-0 md:start-auto md:top-2 h-6 w-6 rounded-full bg-bg-elev border border-gold-soft flex items-center justify-center md:-end-3\"><span class=\"h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-gold\"></span></span><p class=\"text-[10px] tracking-[0.26em] uppercase text-gold\">الانضمام إلى ترشيد</p><h3 class=\"mt-2 font-display text-2xl md:text-3xl text-fg tracking-tight\">ترشيد · كهرماء</h3><p class=\"mt-3 text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-fg-muted max-w-md md:ms-auto\">الانضمام إلى البرنامج الوطني للحفاظ على الطاقة وكفاءتها.</p></div></div></div></li><li class=\"relative\"><div class=\"md:grid md:grid-cols-2 md:gap-12 items-start\"><div class=\"hidden md:block\"></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><div class=\"relative ps-10 md:ps-0 md:ps-12\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"absolute top-1 start-0 md:start-auto md:top-2 h-6 w-6 rounded-full bg-bg-elev border border-gold-soft flex items-center justify-center md:-start-3\"><span class=\"h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-gold\"></span></span><p class=\"text-[10px] tracking-[0.26em] uppercase text-gold\">تنامي القيادة</p><h3 class=\"mt-2 font-display text-2xl md:text-3xl text-fg tracking-tight\">اتساع المسؤولية</h3><p class=\"mt-3 text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-fg-muted max-w-md \">توسّع النطاق ليشمل الاستراتيجية والاتصال والتفاعل المجتمعي.</p></div></div></div></li><li class=\"relative\"><div class=\"md:grid md:grid-cols-2 md:gap-12 items-start\"><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><div class=\"relative ps-10 md:ps-0 md:pe-12 md:text-end\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"absolute top-1 start-0 md:start-auto md:top-2 h-6 w-6 rounded-full bg-bg-elev border border-gold-soft flex items-center justify-center md:-end-3\"><span class=\"h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-gold\"></span></span><p class=\"text-[10px] tracking-[0.26em] uppercase text-gold\">اليوم</p><h3 class=\"mt-2 font-display text-2xl md:text-3xl text-fg tracking-tight\">التعيين رئيساً للقسم</h3><p class=\"mt-3 text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-fg-muted max-w-md md:ms-auto\">قيادة قسم متعدد التخصصات يدعم مهمة ترشيد.</p></div></div></div></li></ol></div></div></section><section id=\"gallery\" class=\"relative py-24 md:py-32\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-10\"><header class=\"mb-12 md:mb-16 max-w-3xl\"><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-5 \"><span class=\"h-px w-8 bg-gold/70\"></span><span class=\"text-xs tracking-[0.28em] uppercase text-gold font-medium\">الإعلام</span></div></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><h2 class=\"font-display text-3xl md:text-5xl leading-[1.1] tracking-tight text-balance text-fg\">لحظات من قلب العمل.</h2></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><p class=\"mt-5 text-base md:text-lg text-fg-muted text-pretty max-w-2xl\">لمحة من الفعاليات والحملات والمبادرات في أرجاء قطر.</p></div></header><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 md:gap-5\"><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><figure class=\"group relative aspect-[4/3] rounded-2xl overflow-hidden glass border border-border\"><img alt=\"الفعاليات الرسمية — حضور رسمي ومنتديات وطنية\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover transition-transform duration-700 ease-out group-hover:scale-[1.03]\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1024px) 32vw, (mi