-fg\">linkedin.com/in/profile</p></div></div></a><div class=\"hairline-gold h-px w-full\"></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4\"><span class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center h-10 w-10 rounded-md bg-bg-elev border border-border-strong text-gold\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-map-pin\"><path d=\"M20 10c0 4.993-5.539 10.193-7.399 11.799a1 1 0 0 1-1.202 0C9.539 20.193 4 14.993 4 10a8 8 0 0 1 16 0\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"10\" r=\"3\"></circle></svg></span><div><p class=\"text-[10px] tracking-[0.26em] uppercase text-fg-subtle\">الموقع</p><p class=\"mt-0.5 text-sm text-fg\">الدوحة، قطر</p></div></div></div></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><div class=\"mt-6 glass rounded-2xl p-6\"><p class=\"text-[10px] tracking-[0.26em] uppercase text-gold\">المكتب</p><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm text-fg-muted leading-relaxed\">يرجى توجيه الاستفسارات الرسمية عبر القنوات الرسمية لكهرماء / ترشيد. هذه الصفحة ملف مهني شخصي وليست قناة اتصال حكومية رسمية.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"lg:col-span-7\"><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><form class=\"glass-strong rounded-2xl p-7 md:p-8 space-y-5\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-5\"><label class=\"block\"><span class=\"text-[10px] tracking-[0.26em] uppercase text-fg-subtle\">الاسم الكامل<!-- --> <span class=\"text-gold\">*</span></span><input type=\"text\" required=\"\" class=\"w-full rounded-md bg-bg-input border border-border text-fg placeholder-fg-faint px-4 py-3 text-sm focus:outline-none focus:border-gold focus:ring-1 focus:ring-gold-soft transition mt-2\" name=\"name\"/></label><label class=\"block\"><span class=\"text-[10px] tracking-[0.26em] uppercase text-fg-subtle\">البريد الإلكتروني<!-- --> <span class=\"text-gold\">*</span></span><input type=\"email\" required=\"\" class=\"w-full rounded-md bg-bg-input border border-border text-fg placeholder-fg-faint px-4 py-3 text-sm focus:outline-none focus:border-gold focus:ring-1 focus:ring-gold-soft transition mt-2\" name=\"email\"/></label></div><label class=\"block\"><span class=\"text-[10px] tracking-[0.26em] uppercase text-fg-subtle\">الموضوع<!-- --> </span><input type=\"text\" class=\"w-full rounded-md bg-bg-input border border-border text-fg placeholder-fg-faint px-4 py-3 text-sm focus:outline-none focus:border-gold focus:ring-1 focus:ring-gold-soft transition mt-2\" name=\"subject\"/></label><label class=\"block\"><span class=\"text-[10px] tracking-[0.26em] uppercase text-fg-subtle\">الرسالة<!-- --> <span class=\"text-gold\">*</span></span><textarea name=\"message\" required=\"\" rows=\"5\" class=\"w-full rounded-md bg-bg-input border border-border text-fg placeholder-fg-faint px-4 py-3 text-sm focus:outline-none focus:border-gold focus:ring-1 focus:ring-gold-soft transition mt-2 resize-none\"></textarea></label><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between gap-4 pt-1\"><p class=\"text-xs text-fg-faint\">بإرسالك للرسالة فأنت توافق على الالتزام بلغة مهنية ومحترمة.</p><button type=\"submit\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-5 h-11 rounded-md text-sm font-medium text-white bg-maroon hover:bg-maroon-strong border border-gold-soft transition-colors disabled:opacity-70 shrink-0\">إرسال الرسالة<!-- --> <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-send flip-rtl\"><path d=\"M14.536 21.686a.5.5 0 0 0 .937-.024l6.5-19a.496.496 0 0 0-.635-.635l-19 6.5a.5.5 0 0 0-.024.937l7.93 3.18a2 2 0 0 1 1.112 1.11z\"></path><path d=\"m21.854 2.147-10.94 10.939\"></path></svg></button></div></form></div></div></div></div></section></main><footer class=\"relative border-t border-border bg-bg\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-10 py-12\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 items-start\"><div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><span class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center h-9 w-9 rounded-md border border-gold-soft bg-bg-elev/60\"><span class=\"font-display text-gold text-sm\">م.ي</span></span><div><p class=\"text-sm text-fg\">مهند اليافعي</p><p class=\"text-xs text-fg-subtle\">رئيس قسم، ترشيد</p></div></div><p class=\"mt-5 text-sm text-fg-muted max-w-xs leading-relaxed\">ملف مهني شخصي — يساهم في جهود الاستدامة والحفاظ على الموارد في قطر من خلال ترشيد وكهرماء.</p></div><div><p class=\"text-[10px] tracking-[0.26em] uppercase text-gold\">تصفّح</p><ul class=\"mt-4 grid grid-cols-2 gap-y-2\"><li><a href=\"#about\" class=\"text-sm text-fg-muted hover:text-fg transition-colors\">نبذة</a></li><li><a href=\"#leadership\" class=\"text-sm text-fg-muted hover:text-fg transition-colors\">القيادة</a></li><li><a href=\"#mission\" class=\"text-sm text-fg-muted hover:text-fg transition-colors\">المهمة</a></li><li><a href=\"#values\" class=\"text-sm text-fg-muted hover:text-fg transition-colors\">القيم</a></li><li><a href=\"#journey\" class=\"text-sm text-fg-muted hover:text-fg transition-colors\">المسيرة</a></li><li><a href=\"#gallery\" class=\"text-sm text-fg-muted hover:text-fg transition-colors\">المعرض</a></li><li><a href=\"#contact\" class=\"text-sm text-fg-muted hover:text-fg transition-colors\">تواصل</a></li></ul></div><div><p class=\"text-[10px] tracking-[0.26em] uppercase text-gold\">المقر</p><p class=\"mt-4 text-sm text-fg\">الدوحة، قطر</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-fg-subtle\">كهرماء · ترشيد</p><p class=\"mt-5 text-sm text-fg-muted\"><a href=\"mailto:contact@example.qa\" class=\"hover:text-fg transition-colors\">contact@example.qa</a></p></div></div><div class=\"mt-12 pt-6 border-t border-border flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-start sm:items-center justify-between gap-3\"><p class=\"text-xs text-fg-faint\">© <!-- -->2026<!-- --> <!-- -->مهند اليافعي<!-- -->.